Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal uColonel Thembeka Mbele uthe abaphenyi basesiteshini samaphoyisa eNanda bathungatha uMnuz Lungisani Derrick Ndlovu osolwa ngecala lokubulala abalamu bakhe ababili ngoDisemba 2016. Uthe uNdlovu ubhekene necala lokubulala uMnuz Mbongiseni Zondo noNksz Funani Zondo (47) abadutshulwa eNamibia, eNanda, ngoDisemba 27, 2016. UNdlovu kuthiwa wazinikela emaphoyiseni, wavela eNkantolo yeMantshi eNtuzuma wanikwa ibheyili kodwa ngo-Okthoba 1 nonyaka uhlulekile ukuvela enkantolo kwabe sekukhishwa incwadi egunyaza ukuboshwa kwakhe. Abangaba nolwazi ukuthi uNdlovu ukuziphi izinkalo bayanxuswa ukuthi bathinte uDetective Sergeant Mthethwa ku-072 259 3518/082 290 5726 noma bashayele inombolo yokubika izigameko zobugebengu u-08600 10111.